summary: NEW npcs for skyrim. Get them now!
descriptionHtml:
This is my second skyrim mod and 5th mod overall and i think its my best mod yet. These are new Creatures and NPCs for you to spawn in for battles or for just looking at them. these are non replacers and are not found as you explore you can only spawn them in.

LIST OF NPCs: 
Elder blade
Elder blade soldier
Elder elf
Daedric elder
Dark brotherhood lord

LIST OF CREATURES:
Elder troll
Elder werewolf
Elder sabre cat
Elder falmer
Elder sphere 
Elder Centurion

TO SPAWN is:   help \"elder\"0 or the name of npc or creature. then player.placeatme (the code)

I dont think there are bugs 

I would suggest downloading manually because of textures  

GO check out my youtube channel for more skyrim (AkumaGamer)
author: Finlaymorgan
